    "title": "Microservices Cascade Failure",
    "description": "Your fintech platform uses a microservices architecture. When the Payment Service slows down under load, threads pile up in the Order Service waiting for responses — eventually bringing both services down. A slow dependency is taking out the whole system. Isolate the failure and keep the platform available.",
